Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.99,0:04:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}这里太吵了！叫我怎麽拍啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.00,0:04:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}如果你早点得到采访她的许可
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我们就用不着造假啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.01,0:04:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}她已经不再是演员了
