Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}这个发疯的老女人.....\n竟然像隐士一样躲藏起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.03,0:05:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}再说一次,我就杀了你！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.97,0:05:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}再怎麽出名的影星也好\n她现在都应该年过70啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.97,0:05:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我是说.....她已经老了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.97,0:05:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}瞧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.98,0:05:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}就是这儿！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.98,0:05:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}喂,不要期望太高啊，我们连.....
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.98,0:05:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}她现在长什麽样子都不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.99,0:05:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}她从来不会变老的！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.99,0:05:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}呃.....
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.00,0:05:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}太太！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.01,0:05:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}请问  原小姐是一个人住的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.01,0:06:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}她已独居多年.....\n唯一的朋友就是书和外边的院子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.02,0:06:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}这是她亲手种的药草茶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.96,0:06:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}可你们很幸运啊.....
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.97,0:06:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}她同意让你们采访
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.97,0:06:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我们可花了不少工夫才找到她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.97,0:06:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}这实在是莫大的面子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.98,0:06:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}可你说有什麽东西要交给太太？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.98,0:06:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}呃.....是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.98,0:06:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}每次她与人结识,地都会震呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.99,0:06:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}美浓,什麽东西会震啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.99,0:06:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}太太,是地都会震呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.99,0:06:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}地震.....今早就有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}难道这不是预示了什麽吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我想时候终於到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.00,0:06:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}你们好,我是  原千代子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.01,0:06:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}这真是值得纪念的一天，我们深感荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.01,0:07:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}哎,别说这种客套话啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.95,0:07:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}您是从.....
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.95,0:07:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}Rootasu电影公司来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.95,0:07:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}那是莲花的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.96,0:07:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}噢,我很喜欢莲花！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.96,0:07:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我知道，这就是我们公司名字的由来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.97,0:07:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}很快就是莲花盛开的季节了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.97,0:07:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}在诗歌里,它们代表着.....
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.97,0:07:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}是的！天真纯洁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.98,0:07:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}对了,立花先生,您提过有东西.....
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.98,0:07:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}噢,是的！很抱歉.....
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.99,0:07:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我一直保存着这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.99,0:07:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}想在找到您的时候,把它交给您
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.00,0:08:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}这麽久以来,我一直想遗忘它
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.94,0:08:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}那钥匙不是能开启什麽很重要的东西吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.95,0:08:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}是啊,它能开启最最重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.95,0:08:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}谢谢你,立花先生？这东西是怎麽找到的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.96,0:08:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}恩.....很多年前,银卫的人找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.97,0:08:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}没想到它还能回到我手中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.99,0:08:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}哎呀,我想连地也在催促我们快开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.99,0:08:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}呃.....是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.00,0:08:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我的一生似乎和地震紧紧相连呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.00,0:09:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我就在地震中出生的，那是1923年
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}在关东大地震中.....
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.94,0:09:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我的父亲一直很想要个孩子\n他死於那场地震
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.95,0:09:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}就好像他用自己的生命换来了我的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.95,0:09:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}可他留下的商店
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.96,0:09:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}让我和母亲过着富足的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.97,0:09:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我在动汤不安中长大\n生活中充满一次又一次的赌博
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}然而,一切最终都转向好的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.99,0:09:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}可我想,少女杂志对我的影响最为重要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.99,0:10:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我常常幻想着终有一天会遇见属於我的王子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.00,0:10:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}是不是就在那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}电影公司发掘了你？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我不知道.....
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.01,0:10:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}银卫的常务董事从一个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.01,0:10:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}正在上学途中的扁鼻子\n小女孩身上看到什麽特质
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.02,0:10:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}实在没有商量的馀地了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.03,0:10:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}一切免谈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.03,0:10:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}认为演员是一种前途堪忧的职业
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.03,0:10:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}前途堪忧？她是这麽认为的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.04,0:10:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}太太！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.04,0:10:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我们的新片将在满洲拍摄\n它将大大鼓舞和激励
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.05,0:10:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}前线的战士和国内的人民
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.05,0:10:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}毫无疑问
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.05,0:10:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}千代子也愿意为报效祖国出一分力吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.05,0:11:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}呃.....
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.99,0:11:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}您也许是对的,可这孩子要去做演员的话\n还太小了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.99,0:11:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}她应该嫁个好人家\n把我们家的店好好经营下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.00,0:11:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我说的没错吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.00,0:11:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}难道说一间糖果店比国家还重要吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.00,0:11:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}难道呆在家里抚养儿女\n就不是女人报效祖国的方式吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.03,0:11:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}国民医疗周 祖国需要你！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.99,0:12:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}呃.....
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.00,0:12:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我们到底在拍什麽啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.00,0:12:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}千代子！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.01,0:12:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我觉得自己像个偷拍狂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.01,0:12:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.02,0:12:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我赶时间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.03,0:12:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}有点不对劲.....
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.03,0:12:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}要置身事外！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.04,0:12:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}他不在这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.04,0:12:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}往那边！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.99,0:13:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}有没见到一个男人经过？\n他拿着一个衣服包着的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.01,0:13:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}他往那边去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.01,0:13:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}快追！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.02,0:13:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.00,0:14:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}包庇这种人还真有勇气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.01,0:14:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}那是什麽人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.01,0:14:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}能让我看看吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.01,0:14:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}这只是初稿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.02,0:14:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}等我回到家就能画完了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.02,0:15:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}到了冬天,眼前是一望无际的雪白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}在那雪的天地中,我觉得逍遥自在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.97,0:15:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我会画完这幅画,直到我冷得受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.97,0:15:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}在那个纯白的世界中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.98,0:15:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}你会觉得自己彷佛来到一个遥远的异世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.99,0:15:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我好想去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}恩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.99,0:15:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}为了报答你,等和平来临的时候\n我会请你去的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.01,0:15:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}满月.....
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.01,0:15:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}明天才是满月
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}可我更喜欢现在的月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.01,0:15:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}满月之後,月亮就开始亏缺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.02,0:16:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}再过14天又会盈满,直到明天.....还有希望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.96,0:16:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.96,0:16:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}可你受伤了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.97,0:16:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我的朋友在满洲战斗着\n虽然画笔算不上什麽武器
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.98,0:16:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}这个？这是开启最最重要的东西的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.98,0:16:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}最最重要的东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.99,0:16:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}猜猜是什麽？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.99,0:16:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}不知道，不过,先别把答案告诉我,直到明天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.00,0:16:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}说定了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.01,0:16:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}说啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.01,0:16:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}你有喜欢的人啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.01,0:16:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}初恋哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.95,0:17:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我.....
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}真是甜蜜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.96,0:17:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}老人也有过青春岁月啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.00,0:17:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}那不就是你带给她的钥匙吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.95,0:18:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}他跑不了多远！快去追！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.96,0:18:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.96,0:18:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}谢天谢地你安然无恙！有小偷潜入了仓库！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.97,0:18:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}他没事,已经到了火车站
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.97,0:18:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}你没事,实在太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.97,0:18:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}那个老店员！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.97,0:19:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}这份工作好辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.97,0:19:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.97,0:19:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.98,0:19:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.98,0:19:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}等等我！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.99,0:19:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我一定会去的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.99,0:19:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我一定会去找你！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.00,0:20:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}真是戏剧化啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.01,0:20:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}这一幕让我哭了53次啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.01,0:20:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}喂喂,什麽时候变成了电影场景啊？！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.02,0:20:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}从那个时候起,我开始拍电影
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.02,0:20:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.02,0:20:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}那具体又是怎麽开始的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.03,0:20:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}还记得银卫的常务董事说过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.03,0:20:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}他们的新片会在满洲拍摄吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.04,0:20:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}满洲！没错！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.04,0:20:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}谢谢你,千代子！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.04,0:20:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我就知道你会同意的
