Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.98,0:29:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}你将永世在不灭的爱火中饱受煎熬！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.99,0:29:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}你骗我！
