Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.99,0:30:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我对你爱至入髓！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.00,0:30:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}总有一天你会明白
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.03,0:30:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}老大！别！
