Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.01,0:33:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}咦呀？！
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.01,0:33:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}敌人！
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.01,0:33:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}看好囚犯！
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.02,0:33:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我是来救你的！
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.02,0:33:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}你永远斗不过我！
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.03,0:33:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}咦？公主会武打吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.98,0:34:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}小心背後！
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.99,0:34:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}干掉她！
