Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.99,0:34:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}你是什麽人？！
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.00,0:34:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}拜托！
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.00,0:34:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我的名字并不重要
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.00,0:34:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}是你！你一直跟着我！
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.01,0:34:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}干掉他！
