Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.00,0:38:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.93,0:39:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}从这里走
