Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.96,0:39:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}从那个时候开始.....
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.97,0:39:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}千代子！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.97,0:39:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}多少留意一下状况,好不好？！
