Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.04,0:40:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}你的钥匙！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.05,0:40:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}保管好,直到我们再次相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.99,0:41:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}那里！快！
