Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.99,0:52:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}战後,我们只能努力求生存
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.99,0:52:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}没有食物,没有衣服.....
