Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.01,0:53:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我是立花源也,您好！
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.02,0:53:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}好好干
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.02,0:53:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}泳子,这是新来的源也
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.02,0:53:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我向来很喜欢您和\n  原千代子之间的对手戏！
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.03,0:54:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}是啊,我总是衬托得她非常突出啊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.97,0:54:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}在她面前不要提千代子啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.97,0:54:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}记住这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.98,0:54:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}在这一行,我们要同时讨好观众和女明星
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.98,0:54:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}下次我教教你该怎麽做
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.98,0:54:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}呃.....是的,先生
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.99,0:54:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}唉,那些话当然很中听
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.01,0:54:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}千代子,电影导演就好比画家
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.02,0:54:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}画家将他喜欢的色彩绘在画布上
