Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.98,0:57:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}老人家需要休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.99,0:57:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}第五次！
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.00,0:57:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}不见了！
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.94,0:58:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}没错了！就是在那一天！
