Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.97,0:58:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}别呆站着啊！快去找！
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.98,0:58:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}是！
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.98,0:58:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}找什麽啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.98,0:58:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}千代子的钥匙！
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.99,0:58:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}原来是泳子拿走的.....
